# Pre-compressed client bundle siblings + source maps (#2054): build-time-only
# artifacts produced by scripts/build-client.sh. NOT committed — their bytes
# depend on the local machine's gzip/brotli library version (cross-contributor
# drift on a byte-identical client.min.js/debug-panel.min.js), and .map files
# additionally embed the absolute filesystem path of the checkout in the
# `sources` field (guaranteed to differ across every clone/worktree).
# client.min.js / debug-panel.min.js themselves stay committed — terser is
# npm-pinned via package-lock.json, so THEIR output is deterministic.
python/djust/static/djust/*.min.js.gz
python/djust/static/djust/*.min.js.br
python/djust/static/djust/*.min.js.map

